{"tid":550204,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得小學啲牙科保健真係好濕鳩","createTime":"2018-02-04T14:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T05:13:05.000Z","uid":75156,"like":42,"dislike":236,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c6ce9ab4bcfa59dc1c7bb3932836644ded856f","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"以前無睇過其他牙醫 覺得20蚊睇一次牙好抵屌 就年年都join<br />\n所有程序一腳踢 檢查牙齒果陣話我有牙菌膜 啲語氣唔知仲以為我有蛀牙 咁我未撚刷牙啊嘛 你做齊所有口腔清潔步驟都唔會確保到24小時都無牙菌膜㗎啦<br />\n洗牙暴力到仆街 正常keep住每年洗牙嘅話係唔會太痛 但係係果度次次洗都係煎熬<br />\n洗完仲要問我 你覺唔覺得棚牙滑咗？<br />\n我舔下棚牙 其實仲係好鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都係鳩應咗佢就算 而且啲牙齒外觀仲係同本身差唔多黃嘅<br />\n到我大個自己出去睇牙醫 屌你原來會有個護士係醫生隔離幫手 而且會間中問我痛唔痛 洗完啲牙明顯白滑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果第日有仔女一定自己帶佢睇私家牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚join呢啲濕鳩保健"},{"pid":"64d122d59a9a8789b109edfae3e20b819b6c4820","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dabc8d0642b159d20a801f7841bfe63c8006cf8","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a67887b43e951e9a1eb00da367f9b7701e3304a","tid":550204,"uid":151926,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"d姑娘好撚惡"},{"pid":"0d3a2b5e270ab7bc3aa404d470bbd6c80440012d","tid":550204,"uid":13518,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"老實講我今年廿中 仲好驚去睇牙<br />\n完完全全係因為小學啲牙科保健<br />\n黎緊book到年中去政府診印睇牙 驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887158f5f03bb9c7940c54d71cdfd6145250db8c","tid":550204,"uid":140094,"like":151,"dislike":3,"score":148,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"d阿嬸好撚仆街 講野好撚刻薄 d態度西到我而家都記得<br />\n細個d牙唔靚 佢帶我去鏡前面刷牙 佢話信唔信我帶你出去比出面d人睇下你d牙有幾肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢搞到以後睇牙都有陰影"},{"pid":"968e28af059e4fc46b284d5d89979f7ce623fb34","tid":550204,"uid":52692,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"試過6-7年冇洗牙跟住去洗<br />\n病撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲記得定期洗"},{"pid":"3d27cf2324c331aa03627f0ba23efb1effc0514f","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"887158f5f03bb9c7940c54d71cdfd6145250db8c","tid":550204,"uid":140094,"like":151,"dislike":3,"score":148,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"d阿嬸好撚仆街 講野好撚刻薄 d態度西到我而家都記得<br />\n細個d牙唔靚 佢帶我去鏡前面刷牙 佢話信唔信我帶你出去比出面d人睇下你d牙有幾肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢搞到以後睇牙都有陰影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"agger 真心唔顧啲小學雞自尊<br />\n換牙時期棚牙緊係唔會靚得去邊㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e83d04e426d95ff5ba34b946d47981e290e1413","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d3a2b5e270ab7bc3aa404d470bbd6c80440012d","tid":550204,"uid":13518,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"老實講我今年廿中 仲好驚去睇牙<br />\n完完全全係因為小學啲牙科保健<br />\n黎緊book到年中去政府診印睇牙 驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"無事嘅 應該得牙科保健果啲先咁廢"},{"pid":"a995d55414bc21b0bed2a64703637c776e8d0768","tid":550204,"uid":73575,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"次次都比d醫生屌到仆街<br />\n雖然自問真係幾唔乾淨<br />\n但真係睇親都怕勁驚果日來臨"},{"pid":"2803fe7ced97a829df027b39a899c53a5ea33020","tid":550204,"uid":29717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"話我有5隻恒齒蛀咗要抆<br />\n第一次抆咗2隻太痛，所以剩低三隻唔敢再去<br />\n結果大個洗牙牙醫話啲牙保養得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874eba483020eceb9f67fb55d1405184607677d0","tid":550204,"uid":148289,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"細個試過要喺嗰度剝牙，<br />\n個醫生整到我勁痛，<br />\n於是我起勢咁踢，<br />\n諗住可以走得甩。<br />\n最後當然要照剝啦，<br />\n但就動用咗五個醫生㩒住我手手腳先成功。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5596d22be9e1a38b750018e38315f974ca11f67","tid":550204,"uid":82542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"細個個時 無刷牙就去<br />\n去到牙醫趕時間 唔比時間我刷左牙先整 之後一路整一路口嗡嗡話我唔刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b7c4b6c42e66186f12b627bbf97635b1049a3a","tid":550204,"uid":72608,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"小學既牙科保健根本就係令細路仔對牙醫感到恐懼既根源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果陣我小1,2去<br />\n<br />\n蛀左隻大牙要拔<br />\n<br />\n拔之前打麻醉針<br />\n<br />\n咁細路仔驚打針好正常,個牙醫又唔識講野分散注意力之類<br />\n<br />\n見到我扭計就一巴掌摑落我塊面到<br />\n<br />\n跟住我呆撚左<br />\n<br />\n後尾係咁喊<br />\n<br />\n好彩而家大個睇私家對牙醫有返信心"},{"pid":"40355002e928d7f1c558c6380679483fcef6d198","tid":550204,"uid":159633,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:57:19.000Z","msg":"細個蛀牙去私家牙醫補牙<br />\n用嘅係高級d、深色嘅補充物料<br />\n跟住join咗小學嘅牙科保健<br />\n佢誤以為嗰d補充物料係蛀牙（因為深色）<br />\n幫我挖曬出黎然後再補番d白色、無咁好嘅物料入去<br />\n仲搞到發炎<br />\n最後要去翻私家牙醫又挖翻出黎再補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從此再無去過"},{"pid":"6469717c77d71095a290d07b9507f445c4c8d25d","tid":550204,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"968e28af059e4fc46b284d5d89979f7ce623fb34","tid":550204,"uid":52692,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"試過6-7年冇洗牙跟住去洗<br />\n病撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲記得定期洗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"咁呢次仆街啦<br />\n我起碼十幾年無睇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚驚呀媽呀"},{"pid":"433528e218c5bf0773610c1dc9f239cec0df1486","tid":550204,"uid":48066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"好懷念，次次有貼紙。"},{"pid":"2e243af41bf7d8cabc225564df41bf7eafaa0ca9","tid":550204,"uid":13518,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學既牙科保健根本就係令細路仔對牙醫感到恐懼既根源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果陣我小1,2去<br />\n<br />\n蛀左隻大牙要拔<br />\n<br />\n拔之前打麻醉針<br />\n<br />\n咁細路仔驚打針好正常,個牙醫又唔識講野分散注意力之類<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">見到我扭計就一巴掌摑落我塊面到<br />\n<br />\n跟住我呆撚左</span><br />\n<br />\n後尾係咁喊<br />\n<br />\n好彩而家大個睇私家對牙醫有返信心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1603dc86afc66ba2a174528743833f8eea43a418","tid":550204,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"好彩跟開我嗰個姑娘好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c73912615940edcbdb42d72b4efb4667e1f4d1","tid":550204,"uid":158906,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"啲牙醫好仆街 特別係啲女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣細個聽到佢用枝嘢係到撩我隻牙<br />\n撩到好似要拆咗我排牙咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要聽到儀器嘅唧唧聲 跟住喊咗出聲 真係勁驚<br />\n個女牙醫西面西語氣咁話：你喊夠未呀 嘈完未呀<br />\n<br />\n從此就好驚睇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2232e92498579f5aa90ba18e94296c88d1cb3b","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"舊登睇過果啲好似根本唔係專業牙醫來 無degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13edd9a527bffd16b89526aa87a0a8474171b124","tid":550204,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5596d22be9e1a38b750018e38315f974ca11f67","tid":550204,"uid":82542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"細個個時 無刷牙就去<br />\n去到牙醫趕時間 唔比時間我刷左牙先整 之後一路整一路口嗡嗡話我唔刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"係呀屌 根本專業牙醫係唔會太在意你有無刷牙先來 佢就係都要搵啲嘢奚落你"},{"pid":"7848f0ee9cd6d58b6d59456447c1c17a254b2fa3","tid":550204,"uid":76514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"記得有一年鼻塞<br />\n佢抽啲水抽得唔好搞到我抖唔到氣<br />\n我同佢講跟住佢兇鳩我話唔合作以後無得洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4636809cf01cbe148bd586a858c23a0d7d6ff99","tid":550204,"uid":96324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"以前牙科保健會有好大陣味&hellip;<br />\n唔知係藥水味定消毒味<br />\n諗起都想嘔 大個睇牙醫又唔會有"},{"pid":"bdab381367ce149630e778a9fb93cd5fde0ea23e","tid":550204,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"私家通常服務好啲，政府你唔好預期太多"},{"pid":"ab730ea18c99d90115c9ec55f288bbf786838e59","tid":550204,"uid":131926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d阿嬸好撚仆街 講野好撚刻薄 d態度西到我而家都記得<br />\n細個d牙唔靚